  <title>gnome-icon-theme-&gnome-icon-theme-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The GNOME Icon Theme package contains an assortment of non-scalable icons
      of different sizes and themes.
    </para>

